article_title: Business Digest: Larramore to head law firm

article_metadata.description: Chattanooa attorney Randall D. Larramore has been elected president of Paty, Rymer & Ulin, P.C., which has now changed its name to Paty, Rymer, Ulin & Larramore, P.C. Larramore received his Master of Public Administration, Master of Business Administration and Juris Doctor from the University of Cincinnati.
